# overview
QBeD (pronounced Q-bed) is a linux based distrubition. This distrbution is based on linux from scratch (LFS) and beyond linux from scratch (BLFS). most of the 
scripts existing in this repository are taken directly from the book.

# why?
* documenting how to create a linux distribution
* creating a tailored distribution(s) for my need
* automating the process of distribution creation


